nett=E2=80=94of =E2=80=9Cbrazen election interference=E2=80=9D and consumer=
 fraud over her November 2 poll showing Kamala Harris winning by three poin=
ts in Iowa. As Trump lawyers Edward Paltzik and Des Moines-based attorney A=
lan R. Ostergren noted in the suit, =E2=80=9CPresident Trump ultimately won=
 Iowa by over thirteen points.=E2=80=9D

